{"tid":1412741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「IT救圖」點可以查動物屋圖則？","createTime":"2019-08-05T07:42:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T07:42:46.000Z","uid":52105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"969edb68872a1366bdedbdebb87088006ba624bf","tid":1412741,"uid":52105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:42:46.000Z","msg":"接近十年前我係一個正苦 online system 搵到敝校某一棟大樓嘅圖則<br />\n\b年代久遠我已經唔記得係點個 system。Google 都搵唔到熟眼嘅。<br />\n<br />\n但係搵到一個未見過嘅「百樓圖網系統」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.hk/tc/residents/housing/private/landrecords/bravo.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fresidents%2Fhousing%2Fprivate%2Flandrecords%2Fbravo.htm&d=7QdSi1Eq0NVbLWVUesVCWFKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=8d2c0051\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.hk/tc/residents/housing/private/landrecords/bravo.htm</a><br />\n有冇巴絲用過呢個「百樓圖網系統」，知唔知有冇建築物嘅圖紙？"}]}